About Us

Lawrence Supplements was established in 2011 after years of personal research and development by its founder John Lawrence.
Disappointed with the lack of availability of safe high quality nutritional supplements, John embarked upon a mission to formulate the best combination of scientifically proven herbs for himself and his cohorts in the adult industry.
That mission led him to all corners of the world to rediscover ancient aphrodisiac secrets and source the purest ingredients for his first proprietary blend - PHGH. PHGH quickly became an industry wide secret of the world's top male adult performers but John was left unsatisfied. He had made his impact upon the adult industry, but it was his decision to share this gift with the world that brought him a real sense of purpose.
He wanted to give this to the people so that all men could have this power, so he left the adult industry and set upon his true mission in life: to help everyday people.
John has been steadfast and dedicated to this undertaking, his new lifework is to produce the highest quality male enhancement formulas with only the best ingredients. John is fully obligated to the safety and satisfaction of the customer and personally stands by a 60 day, 100% money back guarantee.
Lawrence Supplements is committed to developing natural products designed to help men stay healthy and realize their fullest potential.












