                                        bruced
                                    






                                        had these installed 5 month ago. the rears are still working good, but the front sight is barely illuminated. I can't get Tru-Glo to answer any of my e-mails.                                    




Most Helpful Negative Review

                                        Rob Erwin
                                    






                                        We had the sights professionally installed then shot approximately 50 round. The next day the front sight no longer was lighted.I do not believe this to be typical.                                     









