disappointed








        by
                                Chuck,
                                    from NY, United States
                Written on April 12, 2017
    



        I took these sights to a highly respected gunsmith who informed me these TruGlo sights are not worth putting on my Glock 30S.  The front sight does not fit correctly.  The sight has too short of a mounting stem for proper seating which results in an unstable sight.  He installed the sight and showed me how unstable it was. He said  the sight could be secured with a cementing agent but that he highly recommended against doing so.  I chose to return the sights.    




Would recommend:  No 

