Nice to be surprised








        by
                    Baddad,
                                    from CA, United States
                Written on September 6, 2014
    



        These sights really can be seen in the dark.. Compared to my original sights which could not be seen at all in the dark, this was a nice surprise.
When you wake up some night to sounds of someone in your house, you can confidently know that when they come into the room you are in you can put front sight on center mass.
Without night sights your are just going to point a shoot and hope for the best.    




