Best of Lawrence 2017



Drumroll, please ...
Thank you for voting in Best of Lawrence 2017! You and nearly 9,000 others cast more than 300,000 votes over 184 categories during the month of February.

We celebrated the top three placers in each category at our Winners Bash, but those awards represent just a fraction of the businesses, individuals and organizations that make Lawrence such a special place.

Take a moment to scroll through the results and give a hearty congrats to all who were shown love by the people of Lawrence!

